<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10008638>
    dc:description "FIGURE 39. Heteragrion icterops: (a) anterior view of head; (b–c) lateral view of pterothorax; (d, f) mediodorsal view of cercus; (e) dorsal view of anal appendages. ML: medial lobe. Figures e–f provided by Rosser Garrison and Natalia von Ellenrieder." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10008638/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10008640>
    dc:description "FIGURE 40. Heteragrion icterops: (a) anterior view of head; (b) dorsal view of prothorax; (c) dorsal view of pterothorax; (d) lateral view of pterothorax and S1–4; (e) lateral view of S5–10, including the right paraproct; (f) dorsal view of male type, with the original labels at RBINS." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10008640/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10008642>
    dc:description "FIGURE 41. Ventral view of male genital fossae, showing the accessory structures and secondary genitalia of: (a–b) Heteragrion icterops, and (c) H. inca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10008642/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10008644>
    dc:description "FIGURE 42. Heteragrion inca: (a–c) anterior view of head; (d) lateral view of pterothorax; (e–f, h) mediodorsal view of cercus; (g, i) close up showing the two MP ridges above ML; (c) adapted from the drawing by Williamson (1919). MP: medial portion of cercus; ML: medial lobe. Figures h–i provided by Rosser Garrison and Natalia von Ellenrieder." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10008644/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

